  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Byron has a really fresh and stylish look. It's brand new, so has everything you need for a comfortable stay and the fantastic views of the Ligurian Riviera will make your summer holiday incredibly memorable!</p>
<h2>Near the beach and the centre of Lerici</h2>
<p>The location's fantastic, within five minutes walk from the centre of town, so you'll be able to check out the local bars, restaurants and shops easily. The beach is just opposite the hotel and in high season hotel guests get a special rate on beach services, including the use of sunbeds and umbrellas (payable locally).</p>
<h2>Great for active holidays</h2>
<p>This hotel's a great choice if you want an activity filled holiday. Not only will you have easy access to walking trails, but you'll also be just a stones throw away from tennis, golf, cycling and sailing spots (payable locally). This is a really fun place for a holiday, and you can't beat those sea views!</p>]]></description>
