  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Comfort Rooms </strong>sleep up to three people (third bed is available on request, please call to book).</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms </strong>sleep two people and have a balcony, with a side sea view.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are more spacious and sleep up to three people. They have a balcony and a side sea view. These rooms are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms for sole use</strong> are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Air-conditioning</li>
<li>Shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available on request.</p>
<p><strong>Local fees and ta</strong><strong>xes:</strong></p>
<p>A tourist tax of €1.50 per person per night is payable locally (max. 5 night stay, not applicable to children under 12 years old).</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
